{"type":"message","id":"8b978eb7","parentId":"7295e977","timestamp":"2026-05-29T06:03:56.371Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人让我开Bug单。这是个耗时任务（TAPD 提单需要 Playwright 跑浏览器，30s+），按 TOOLS.md 的规则应该开子 session 处理。\n\n不过先让我读一下 TAPD 自动提单的 Skill，确保我按正确流程来。\n\nWait, let me check my rules:\n1. 检查本地 skill 列表 → 有 `feishu-doc`, `feishu-drive`, `feishu-perm`, `feishu-wiki`, `skill-creator`, `taskflow`, `taskflow-inbox-triage` 这几个。没有一个叫 tapd-bug-create 的 skill。\n\n但是 MEMORY.md 提到：\n- \"TAPD 自动提单 Skill\" 路径 `~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/tapd-bug-create/`\n- \"TAPD自动提单（进行中 - 2026-05-15）\"\n\n看 available_skills 列表，没有 tapd-bug-create 这个 skill。但 MEMORY.md 里提到了 skill 路径。让我再查一下这个路径是否存在。\n\nActually, I should check the available_skills list again:\n- feishu-doc\n- feishu-drive\n- feishu-perm\n- feishu-wiki\n- skill-creator\n- taskflow\n- taskflow-inbox-triage\n\nNone of these match \"tapd-bug-create\". So I should proceed based on what I know from MEMORY.md and TOOLS.md about TAPD bug creation.\n\nFrom MEMORY.md:\n- TAPD 自动提单 Skill路径：`~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/tapd-bug-create/`\n- 工作区 ID：`31253609`（月圆之夜）\n- 创建缺陷 URL：`/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/add`\n- 模板 ID：`1131253609001000011`\n- 用户 ID：叶枝君=`1415287364`，周以天=`1166740146`\n- 表单字段：title/priority/version/module/branch/handler\n- 提交按钮：`#_view`\n- 文件上传：`#file_input`\n- 处理人必须包含周以天\n\nBut since the skill isn't in available_skills, I won't read it.\n\nNow, this is a >10s task, so I should use sessions_spawn to create a sub-agent. Let me prepare the info:\n\nBug title: CCG 更新后游戏内音效大量缺失\nContent: 三位玩家反馈，CCG 更新完成后，游戏内音效明显减少/缺失。\nModule: 音频 (or maybe CCG)\nHandler: 周以天（必须包含）\nPriority: 重要\n\nWait, I don't have the player's screenshot since the image wasn't found. But let me proceed with what we have.\n\nI'll spawn a sub-agent with context=fork since it needs the current transcript context (to know the bug details).\n\nActually, looking at TOOLS.md:\n> **提 Bug / 需求单（TAPD）** → `sessions_spawn` 子 session | Playwright 跑浏览器，耗时 30s+\n\nSo yes, spawn a sub-agent.\n\nLet me read the tapd-bug-create skill first to see if there's relevant info.\n\nActually wait - MEMORY.md says the skill path is `~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/tapd-bug-create/` but it's not in available_skills. Maybe it's an old skill that wasn't properly registered. Let me check if the directory exists.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好嘞，开 Bug 单，耗时任务我走子 session 处理。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_6eFRYxpI0ZXNQIUOtwmc0179","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"if (Test-Path \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\tapd-bug-create\\SKILL.md\") { Write-Output \"EXISTS\" } else { Write-Output \"NOT_FOUND\" }","timeout":3}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2250,"output":892,"cacheRead":19584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22726,"cost":{"input":0.000315,"output":0.00024976,"cacheRead":0.000548352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001113112}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780034628504,"responseId":"fbd8d750-76e7-4a85-9e22-2c5adc479d01"}}
